Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,东西都准备好了. 他们正在\N北方大酒店等我们.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's set. They're waiting for us\Nat the Great Northern.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:46.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 一所木制大房子,\N被树木围绕着.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a large house made of wood,\Nsurrounded by trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:51.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在里面的每一个房间\N都一模一样,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The house is filled with many rooms\Neach alike,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:57.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,却被不同的灵魂所占据\N夜复一夜.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but occupied by different souls\Nnight after night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:03.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 房客都安排到大堂了?\N- 都鼎力合作.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The guests will be in the lobby?\N- Full cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:07.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,豪克, 你拿到哈罗德·史密斯公寓\N的搜查令了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk, you got that warrant\Nfor Harold Smith's apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:10.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我喝完这咖啡\N马上就去.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my way\Nas soon as l finish my coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,豪克, 戈登曾提到\N那几页纸--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk, Gordon has mentioned\Npages--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:16.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我提到过在血毛巾旁\N发现了几页纸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What l mentioned were pages\Nfound near the bloody towel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:18.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就在犯案地点\N火车轨下面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,down the train tracks\Nfrom the crime site
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是从一本日记上撕下来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were from a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜·海沃德\N说过哈罗德·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna Hayward\Nspoke of Harold Smith
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:25.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有劳拉·帕尔默\N的一本秘密日记.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having a secret diary\Nof Laura Palmer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:29.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能很重要.\N你去查查看.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could be important.\NLet me know what you dig up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:32.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戈登, 我知道你--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gordon, l understand you're--?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戈登, 我知道你\N还要赶去俄勒冈州的本德,是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gordon, l understand\Nyou're on your way to Bend, Oregon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:39.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要经过俄勒冈州本德,\N公事, 高度机密.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm over to Bend, Oregon,\Nofficial business, real hush-hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们大家好运.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 库.\N- 戈登.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Coop.\N- Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好好照顾迈克.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能认识你们真是太好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was real nice meeting you fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 警长.\N- 路上小心, 长官.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sheriff.\N- Safe journey, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:15.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警长? 警长!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff? Sheriff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:20.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警长, 这是什么意思?\N到底怎么回事儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff, what's the meaning of this?\NWhat the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:28.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有谁能告诉我\N这儿到底在搞什么鬼名堂?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will somebody please tell me\Nwhat the hell is happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在这儿搞什么鬼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗德·史密斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harold Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,早安.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 早安, 亲爱的.\N- 早安, 马蒂.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good morning, dear.\N- Good morning, Maddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰姨父.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉姨妈.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aunt Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:30.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,坐. 噢, 好, 喝点咖啡.\N好.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit. Oh, good, you got some coffee.\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:35.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 昨晚睡得好吗?\N- 很好. 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you sleep well?\N- Very well. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很喜欢留在这儿\N和这儿的一切.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've really enjoyed my stay\Nand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:52.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得该是时候\N回家了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l really feel like it's time\Nfor me to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,回密苏拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Missoula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:02.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有自己的工作和公寓.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've got my job and my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:09.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...该回到我自己的生活了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...miss having a life of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:16.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以,我想或者明天\N就开车回家了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l think l'll probably be driving\Nback home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明天?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:22.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 我们会非常\N挂念你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we are going to miss you\Nvery much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:27.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但我们完全理解.\N- 真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But we also understand completely.\N- You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:30.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的.\N- 我们理解. 是, 我们理解.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We do.\N- We do. Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有你在这儿\N对我们真是太重要了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have been\Nsuch a wonderful help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是, 但现在她也该为\N自己想想了, 宝贝.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but now she has to think\Nabout herself, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:43.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她有她自己的人生.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且, 你会回来探望我们的,\N对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you'll come back and visit,\Nwon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 这个当然了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:51.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会经常飞奔回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll come galloping back often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你把密苏拉讲的好像\N在天涯海角似的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not like Missoula\Nwas at the far end of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:56.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不.\N- 怎么会.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No.\N- Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 那就好.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,记住\N我们非常爱你.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just know that we love you\Nvery much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:10.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱你们.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:34.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿, 那是什么, 一本笔记?\N- 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, what's that, a note?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"我是一个寂寞的灵魂."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''l'm a lonely soul.''
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的家伙.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:52.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好安迪\N没在这儿看到这一幕.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a good thing\NAndy didn't see this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来看看这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"这是劳拉·帕尔默的日记."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''This is the diary of Laura Palmer.''
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有线索了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:41.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看, 我们一共有1,014美元\N的帐单要付.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we have bills here\Nthat total $1 ,01 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,算上保险赔偿金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lncluding the insurance money
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that leaves you with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,42美元.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forty-two dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:56.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 42美元.\N- 是个好开始啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Forty-two dollars.\N- That's a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,42元一个月?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forty-two dollars for the month?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎么过啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am l gonna make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就靠这42美元\N怎么够我们过一个月?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to survive\Non $42 a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:08.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们? 雪莉, 我不能老骗\N我爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We? Shelly, l can't keep telling\Nmy mom and dad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说我每晚都在\N麦克家过.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that l'm spending the night\Nat Mike's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,几点了?\N今天的经济课我要迟到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?\Nl'm missing Economics as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"我们" 是指我和里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''We'' meant me and Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 你说过\N你会照顾我们的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, you said\Nyou were gonna take care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会, 雪莉. 我会的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am, Shelly. l am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你\N把那项链拿回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you\Nto take the necklace back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没必要那样做.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你把那项链拿回来.\N我们需要钱.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to take the necklace back.\NWe need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:40.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 你还是先\N留着那项链吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, you're gonna\Nkeep this necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都不知道究竟几时\N才有足够的资格戴上它?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When am l ever gonna feel\Nglamorous enough to wear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给里欧洗澡的时候戴?\N还是给他喂燕麦洲的时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving Leo a bath?\NFeeding him his oatmeal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那他的卡车呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:56.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,反正他再也做不成\N公路飞车侠了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna be cannonballing\Ndown the highway anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 被警察扣押了.\N- 那我们去拿回来啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:11:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The police impounded it.\N- We can get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说那卡车\N是运毒工具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said if it was used\Nin the commission of a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要充公.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it becomes property of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:09.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但他还没有被起诉啊.\N- 规矩又不是我定的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He wasn't charged with anything.\N- l didn't make the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在怪我吗\N好像是我的错了似的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's like you're blaming me\Nfor something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:17.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有怪你. 别这样了.\N冷静点.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not blaming you. Come on.\NTake it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:23.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧以前和很多人一起\N搞过很多东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo was into a lot of different stuff\Nwith a lot of different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,应该赚了不少钱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in it for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:30.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 瞧瞧你.\N你真的以为里欧有很多钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, look around you.\NYou really think that Leo had money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 我觉得是.\N看看这支票本,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l do.\NHaving a look at this checkbook,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他不可能\N存在银行里.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think he ever stepped foot\Ninto a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定把钱藏在\N什么地方了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been hiding it\Nsomewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他醒过来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:50.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,新鞋子.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 他又醒过来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他不是醒, 雪莉.\N- 但他说话了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He ain't alive, Shelly.\N- But he talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是-- 打嗝而已.\N他胃里可能有气.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's only-- That was a burp.\NHe probably has gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:23.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说那是打嗝?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that a burp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,新鞋子.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:36.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他最近刚巧买了\N新鞋子?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he buy any shoes lately\Nby any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他只叫我拿一双靴子\N去修理.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had me take in a pair of boots\Nfor repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:45.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 几时?\N- 上星期.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- When?\N- Last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:49.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 收据还在吗?\N- 在, 干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Have you got a receipt?\N- Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:52.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.\N雪莉, 去吧收据拿来.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.\NShelly, go get that receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,新鞋子.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想要新鞋子吗, 里欧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some new shoes, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:08.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们想要的,\N我就把整个鞋店买下来给你.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us what we want,\Nl'll buy you the whole damn shoe store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,新鞋子.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:25.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸, 关于『单眼杰克』的事\N我都知道了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, l know about\NOne-Eyed Jack's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:31.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很明白\N你想说什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure l don't know\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道布莱奇,\N我知道埃默里·巴提斯,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know about Blackie,\Nl know about Emory Battis,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还知道朗尼特,\N和劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know about Ronette,\Nand l know about Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:47.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里. 看见你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was there. l saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得普鲁登斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember Prudence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,带着白色小面具的，那就是我.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wore a little white mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有几个问题需要问你.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,问吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:18.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你开『单眼杰克』\N多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you owned\NOne-Eyed Jack's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:24.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,5年了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道劳拉在那里工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know Laura worked there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她只在那儿呆过一阵子.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was only there for a brief time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是问你知不知道?\N- 知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you know?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:37.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有怂恿过她\N去那里工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you in any way encourage her\Nto work there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:41.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有. 我都不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. l had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:44.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她自己要求说想在\N百货店商场工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked if she could work\Nin the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,巴提斯没问过我就把她去送去那里了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battis sent her without my knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你和她睡过了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:06.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是你杀了她吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:43.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱她.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:12.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛, 能和你\N讲几句吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Norma, can l talk to you\Nfor a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:16.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然. 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:22.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自从里欧回家后，所有事都...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Leo coming home and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...我应该留在家里\N看护他的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l'm supposed to be there\Nto watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:30.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且估计\N要全天候了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like\Nit's gonna be a full-time thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:37.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,必须把工作辞了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that l have to quit my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,总之先过一段时间吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a little while anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我好难过.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之前我自己还保证过\N不会这样做的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l promised myself\Nl wasn't gonna do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的, 甜心.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉糟透了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just feel so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:09.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你, 也爱在这儿工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love you. l love working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我实在不想令你失望.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't wanna let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会让我失望的.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:25.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧, 雪莉, 你有自己的生活\N也有自己的事要操心.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Shelly, you've got your own life\Nto worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我这儿没问题的.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll be fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:32.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的吗?\N- 真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you sure?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:35.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 你要照顾好自己.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you look after yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,登你安顿好,\N就可以回来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're ready,\Nyou can come right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:42.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一切如常\N就像你从没离开过.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt'll be like you haven't even\Nmissed a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:46.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会让我重新回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll let me come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:50.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是到别的地方工作\N试试看,我可不饶你.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just try to take a job someplace\Nelse and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知该说什么好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:03.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都别说了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:19.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉他了\N我原来打算和爸妈去旅行,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l told him l'd been traveling\Nwith my parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:23.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我现在想先报读\N春季班.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now l wanted to register\Nfor spring semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 小艾艾, 我们坐柜台这边吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Eddie, let's sit at the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:30.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我太想喝巧克力奶昔了,\N你想喝不?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm just dying for a chocolate shake,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:33.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 诺玛.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:37.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快说, 你在这工作\N多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how long have you\Nbeen working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 到4月就满20年了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's 20 years this April.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 你别开玩笑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you kidder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她太搞笑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a kidder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:54.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 才6周而已,\N对不对, 诺玛?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's been about six weeks,\Nisn't that right, Norma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大约6周.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About six weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:03.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢, 啊, 对.\N- 嗯, 你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, yeah, that's right.\N- Well, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当你给爸妈硬是拉去欧洲\N或别处玩一个月,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your parents drag you off\Nto Europe or someplace for a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:11.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之后, 你再回来,\N就会像离开很久似的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then, when you get back,\Nit's like you've been away forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2杯巧克力奶昔,\N谢谢, 诺玛.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two chocolate shakes,\Nplease, Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:22.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要咖啡.\N- 我要加生奶油.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Coffee for me.\N- Extra whipped cream on mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:28.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你叫什么?\N- 雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's your name?\N- Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:33.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在学校和我同班么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in our class at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不是.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:44.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿奶昔和咖啡.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll get the shake and coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:53.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 欧洲?\N- 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Europe?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸妈爱上那里了\N现在还呆在那儿呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents loved it so much\Nthey're still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:02.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还说我可以\N呆在小艾艾家呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they said it was okay\Nfor me to stay over at Eddie's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那房子到底是我父母的\N还是我的, 小艾艾?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it your parents' house\Nor mine, Eddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:15.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 说, 诺玛,\N你会不会生气或别的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, say, Norma,\Nyou're not mad or anything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:20.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为小艾艾正和我约会,\N你会不高兴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because Eddie's sort of taking me out,\Nare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:24.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你和艾德? 不. 不.\N我怎么会呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Ed? No. No.\NWhy should l be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:28.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 没别的.\N因为小艾艾告诉我你刚分手了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no reason.\NEddie told me you broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:36.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...就是太为他陶醉了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l'm just so sweet on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:44.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他实在太迷人了,不是吗?\N- 纳丁.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lsn't he just the dreamiest?\N- Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:50.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真等不及\N足球季快点到就好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't wait\Nfor the start of football season.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你觉得呢?\N- 不. 我也等不及了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can you?\N- No. Can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:00.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好开心.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢, 纳丁.\N- 噢, 天啊, 对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, Nadine.\N- Oh, God, l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:07.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是怎么做到的?\N- 又给我压爆了一个.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How'd you do that?\N- There goes another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个玻璃杯之前\N肯定有裂痕.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must've been a crack\Nin this glass from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 天啊.\N- 那不算.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Golly.\N- Don't count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近老笨手笨脚的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so clumsy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:20.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,连我自己都不敢相信.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can hardly believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:23.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 去拿止血贴,\N我去拿毛巾.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, get those Band-Aids,\Nand l'll get a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 小艾艾.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Eddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:41.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能亲吻你至死为止.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could just kiss you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 你小子, 纳丁.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:16.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她还在店里. 雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think she's at the diner. Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:19.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:28.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那, 麦克.\N全新里欧·强生.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is, Mike.\NThe late Leo Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:44.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是汉克干的?\N- 不是他是谁.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hank did this?\N- He sure as hell did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:47.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他就站在那扇窗户\N开枪射进来.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shot him through that window\Nright there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:52.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 我去鞋店了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, l went to the shoe shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:56.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我给他们看收据,\N然后你看他们给我什么了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l showed them the ticket,\Nand look what they gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:03.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 新鞋子.\N- 才不是, 你这傻帽, 是旧鞋.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- New shoes.\N- No, you knucklehead, old shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:06.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 他念念不忘鞋子这事儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, he gets pretty fixated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.64,0:23:09.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我到希望他永远惦记这事儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope he gets permanently fixated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:13.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我太他妈的了解你了, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know you too damn well, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子里肯定有鬼名堂,\N没错吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about these shoes,\Nisn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:20.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有些事\N跟这些鞋子有关.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something\Nwith these shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:28.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说过有人, 你知道吗,\N在他们的靴子里塞东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard about people, you know,\Nmuling stuff in their boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:30.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啥, 你以为\N我没检查过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you think\Nl didn't check these out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:33.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你有锤子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you get a hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:36.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别乱跑, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go anywhere, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:56.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我的天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是什么, 一盘磁带?\N- 别碰.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is that, a tape?\N- Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:15.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别再吐口水了, 伙计.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit spitting, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:21.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,咳, 又不是钱.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not money.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.29,0:24:25.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但谁知道呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.54,0:24:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.07,0:24:43.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 下午2:47.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.33,0:24:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, it's 2:4 7 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.86,0:24:46.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在警局的\N会议室里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.13,0:24:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm in the conference room\Nat the sheriff's station
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.21,0:24:49.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在看劳拉·帕尔默\N残存的秘密日记.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.47,0:24:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the remains\Nof Laura Palmer's secret diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.30,0:24:51.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很棘手\N它已经残缺不全了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great deal of it\Nhas been mutilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.66,0:24:53.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很多我之前已经\N推测过的论点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.94,0:24:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much of what l've been able\Nto decipher
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.49,0:24:55.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都得到了\N独臂人的论证.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.77,0:24:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,supports the contention\Nof the one-armed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.06,0:24:59.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们一再显示了\N鲍勃的存在.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.31,0:24:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are repeated references\Nto a Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.41,0:25:02.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从她青春期开始\N他就一直存在并威胁着她.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.68,0:25:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a threatening presence\Nin her life from early adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.55,0:25:08.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的信息还显示\N虐待和性骚扰是家常便饭.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.82,0:25:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are intimations of abuse\Nand molestation on a regular basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.43,0:25:12.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他还提到,\N在多个场合中,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.69,0:25:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is referred to,\Non more than one occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.48,0:25:14.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以她父亲朋友的身份出现.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.76,0:25:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a friend of her father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.14,0:25:16.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我刚刚才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.43,0:25:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l just uncovered this entry
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.84,0:25:19.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她死前\N2周写道:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.13,0:25:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dated less than two weeks\Nbefore her death:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:24.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"终有一天我会把\N本·荷恩公诸于众.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.47,0:25:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Someday l'm gonna tell the world\Nabout Ben Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.60,0:25:28.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让大家知道\N本·荷恩到底是个什么样的人."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.87,0:25:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna tell them\Nwho Ben Horne really is.''
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.96,0:25:32.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请进?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.21,0:25:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.80,0:25:37.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 欧蕊.\N- 我必须要见你.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.08,0:25:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Audrey.\N- l had to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.97,0:25:41.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很抱歉打断你工作.\N- 你现在感觉怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.22,0:25:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l'm sorry if l'm interrupting you.\N- How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.33,0:25:44.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我和父亲谈过了.\N- 如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.59,0:25:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l spoke with my father.\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.12,0:25:47.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他和她睡过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.36,0:25:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was sleeping with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.78,0:25:49.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.03,0:25:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.96,0:25:53.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道他们有多久,\N可能有好一阵子了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.23,0:25:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know for how long,\Nmaybe quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.88,0:25:55.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的神啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.17,0:25:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.01,0:25:58.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她当时在『单眼杰克』,\N那儿工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.30,0:25:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was up at One-Eyed Jack's,\Nworking there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.11,0:26:02.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我发现,\N原来那里是属于他的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.37,0:26:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he owns the place,\Nthat's what l found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.24,0:26:05.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他亲口告诉你的?\N- 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.51,0:26:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He told you this?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.04,0:26:09.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.31,0:26:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.13,0:26:11.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.38,0:26:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.57,0:26:14.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么做?\N你要逮捕他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.82,0:26:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?\NAre you gonna arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.01,0:26:19.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 我不想你和任何人\N说这件事，一个字也别提.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.26,0:26:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, l don't want you to say\Na word about this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.85,0:26:25.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的.\N- 很好. 现在, 先回家.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.13,0:26:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay.\N- Okay. Now, go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.14,0:26:35.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.41,0:26:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.93,0:26:38.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别用药，他会指引你.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.21,0:26:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without chemicals he points.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.06,0:26:42.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今早在北方大酒店,\N当那个人走进房间时
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.34,0:26:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning at the Great Northern,\NMike reached for his arm and fainted
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.64,0:26:46.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克伸手去摸断臂那边\N而且还忽然变得很虚弱.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.88,0:26:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just when a certain person\Nwalked into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.04,0:26:50.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我们需要一份搜查令了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.29,0:26:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, we need a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.52,0:26:53.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一份拘捕本杰明·荷恩\N的搜查令.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.76,0:26:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warrant for the arrest\Nof Benjamin Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.64,0:27:07.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好消息, 托吉麻辣先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.90,0:27:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good news, Mr. Tojamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.56,0:27:10.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟, 杰利,\N和你在大阪的人谈过了,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.81,0:27:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother, Jerry,\Nspoke to your people in Osaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.48,0:27:12.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也核对过你提供\N的东京银行的资料,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.74,0:27:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,checked your references\Nat the Tokyo bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.14,0:27:16.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对于你向我们提出的计划,\N我的好朋友,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.41,0:27:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the answer to your proposal,\Nmy good friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.36,0:27:19.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一致通过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.62,0:27:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a big thumbs up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.72,0:27:23.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也感谢你的迅速行动.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.99,0:27:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your promptness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.47,0:27:26.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们太高兴了\N简直无法用言语来形容,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.72,0:27:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking for the entire community\Nof Twin Peaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.56,0:27:28.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我谨代表双峰镇全体居民
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.79,0:27:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l cannot tell you how pleased we are
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.13,0:27:32.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,热烈欢迎你\N加入格斯伍计划.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.39,0:27:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to welcome you\Ninto the Ghostwood fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.75,0:27:35.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.97,0:27:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.23,0:27:40.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 合同. 请你过目.\N- 我会尽快审批,和--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.50,0:27:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Contract. For your perusal.\N- And a fast approval l--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.11,0:27:43.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警局.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.41,0:27:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.00,0:27:49.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是干什么?\N- 警察办案.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.28,0:27:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is this?\N- This is police business.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.44,0:27:51.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请你跟我们走一趟.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.72,0:27:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.09,0:27:55.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好. 但我正巧在开会.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.35,0:27:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. l happen to be in a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.27,0:27:58.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能给我个合理的解释吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.52,0:27:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be a little more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.24,0:28:04.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是劳拉·帕尔默谋杀案\N的头号嫌疑人了.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.49,0:28:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wanted for questioning\Nin the murder of Laura Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.56,0:28:06.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个解释够合理了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.80,0:28:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that specific enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.53,0:28:15.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你神经病. 简直是神经.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.80,0:28:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're insane. lnsane.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.97,0:28:18.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托吉麻辣先生, 我肯定这是个\N极其严重的误会.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.27,0:28:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tojamura, l'm sure that this\Nis some dreadful mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.63,0:28:20.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是乖乖合作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.88,0:28:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come quietly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.68,0:28:23.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还是要我们用手铐拉着你\N穿过酒店大堂呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.95,0:28:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or we can drag you through your lobby\Nin handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.82,0:28:27.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀, 你们在恶意\N玩弄我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.05,0:28:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper, is this some sort\Nof sick joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.91,0:28:30.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是,\N我警告你,我可认识很多高官.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.15,0:28:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if it is,\Nl know people in high places.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.00,0:28:33.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好照他说的办.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.29,0:28:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better do what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.02,0:28:40.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滚.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.30,0:28:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.16,0:28:44.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滚出这里. 滚开, 快滚.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.40,0:28:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here. Go on, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.99,0:28:47.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去吃三文治了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.30,0:28:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna go out for a sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.61,0:28:51.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不! 不!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.87,0:28:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.27,0:28:54.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.54,0:28:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.36,0:28:58.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.65,0:28:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.24,0:29:01.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.52,0:29:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.64,0:29:06.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 你们不能这样对我.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.89,0:29:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You can't do this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.95,0:29:11.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 既成事实了.\N- 你们--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.19,0:29:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt's already done.\N- You--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.18,0:30:14.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.42,0:30:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.81,0:30:43.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先把他关到拘留室.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.09,0:30:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him down to the holding cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:19.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道将会发生什么\N或什么时候发生,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.85,0:31:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what will happen\Nor when,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.20,0:31:23.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但猫头鹰们\N会会出现在公路小屋.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.46,0:31:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are owls\Nin the Roadhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.04,0:31:27.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,公路小屋.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.30,0:31:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roadhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.53,0:31:34.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有事要发生了,\N是吗, 玛格利特?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.80,0:31:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is happening,\Nisn't it, Margaret?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.45,0:31:37.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.71,0:31:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.83,0:32:30.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,喂, 看着我, 老兄,\N你给我小心点.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.09,0:32:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, look here, buster,\Nyou just watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.10,0:32:35.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自从我们相遇,\N我就被你莫名其妙的吸引了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.36,0:32:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the moment we met,\Nl have been strangely attracted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.28,0:32:38.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好马上给我滚出这里,\N先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.53,0:32:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just better get the hell out of here,\Nmister.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.98,0:32:42.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的双眼,\N那么温暖...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.24,0:32:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something about your eyes,\Nso warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.99,0:32:44.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...和深沉.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.24,0:32:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.91,0:32:48.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝如天际
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.14,0:32:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And blue as the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.53,0:32:56.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货, 是我. 是我啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.78,0:32:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy, it's me. lt's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.02,0:32:59.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.29,0:32:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.34,0:33:05.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你样子好可怕.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.60,0:33:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.74,0:33:12.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.04,0:33:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.24,0:33:17.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真 太可怕了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.47,0:33:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.70,0:34:55.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}告诉你的心我是唯一{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.93,0:34:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell your heart that l'm the one
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.20,0:35:06.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}告诉你的心那就是我{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.45,0:35:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell your heart it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.29,0:35:22.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道哈罗德·史密斯的事了吗?\N- 知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.56,0:35:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You heard about Harold Smith?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.56,0:35:28.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是任何人的错.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.80,0:35:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not anybody's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.35,0:35:29.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他有病.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.61,0:35:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a sick man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.92,0:35:33.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他的内心一定在某种程度上很受伤\N而我却没能帮助他.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.18,0:35:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think he was hurt inside\Nin a way l couldn't figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.50,0:35:38.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人内心都受过伤.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.75,0:35:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's hurt inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.77,0:35:46.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他的一生都在那个房子里,\N我却亵渎了它,毁了它.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.05,0:35:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His whole life was in that house,\Nand l violated that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.57,0:35:50.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想找到\N有关劳拉的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.83,0:35:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just trying to find out\Nabout Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.41,0:35:57.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯, 他死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.70,0:35:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.81,0:36:01.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他不该遭那个罪.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.07,0:36:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't deserve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.73,0:36:07.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}影子在我屋里{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.97,0:36:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow in my house
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.87,0:36:13.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那个人, 他有棕色的双眼{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.11,0:36:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man, he has brown eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.67,0:36:16.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜鲁门警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.92,0:36:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.86,0:36:25.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}爱让我感动{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.13,0:36:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love moves me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.00,0:36:33.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我要你\N在我心里来回摇荡{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.27,0:36:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you\NRockin' back inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.28,0:36:38.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我要你\N在我心里来回摇荡{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.54,0:36:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you\NRockin' back inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.64,0:36:40.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马蒂要走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.88,0:36:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maddy's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.51,0:36:44.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.78,0:36:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.43,0:36:48.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 她准备回家了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.68,0:36:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's gonna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.23,0:36:54.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就怪了.\N她从来没向我提起过.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.49,0:36:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.\NShe never said anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.39,0:37:13.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}告诉你的心你让我哭泣了{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.67,0:37:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell your heart you make me cry
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.72,0:37:25.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}告诉你的心不会让我死去{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.98,0:37:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell your heart don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.22,0:37:32.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我要你\N在我心里来回摇荡{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.49,0:37:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you\NRockin' back inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.10,0:37:40.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我要你\N在我心里来回摇荡{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.36,0:37:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you\NRockin' back inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.34,0:37:46.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在我心里来回摇荡{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.57,0:37:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockin' back inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.79,0:37:54.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}影子在我屋里{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.05,0:37:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow in my house
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.73,0:38:08.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}尘埃到处飞舞{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.03,0:38:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dust is dancing in the space
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.85,0:38:19.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}狗和鸟儿彼此远离{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.11,0:38:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog and bird are far away
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.70,0:38:33.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}日初日落\N日日如是{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.95,0:38:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun comes up and down\NEach day
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.44,0:38:52.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它又发生了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.67,0:38:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt is happening again.
